headline: Meet Your New Magenta BFF: T-Mobile and Baby Three Release Limited-Edition Plush Collab
summary: BELLEVUE, Wash., December 04, 2025--This holiday season, T-Mobile (NASDAQ: TMUS) is teaming up with viral toy phenomenon Baby Three to launch the "No Filter Series" — an exclusive plush collab guaranteed to melt hearts — arriving at T-Mobile stores in Times Square and Alderwood Mall in the Greater Seattle Area on Dec. 13.
